{"id":818,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":818,"title":"Jeremiah 49","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 49"],[".studySummary",["i","Judgment and destruction will come upon the people of Ammon, Edom, Kedar, Hazor, and Elam."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.1","order":"02.25.049.54084"},["b","1"],"Concerning the Ammonites, thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Hath Israel no sons? hath he no heir? why",["i","then"],"doth their king inherit Gad, and his people dwell in his cities?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.2","order":"02.25.049.54085"},["b","2"],"Therefore, behold, the days come, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that I will cause an alarm of war to be heard in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Rabbah"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Ammonites"],"; and it shall be a desolate heap, and her",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"daughters"],"shall be burned with fire: then shall Israel be heir unto them that were his heirs, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.3","order":"02.25.049.54086"},["b","3"],"Howl, O Heshbon, for Ai is spoiled: cry, ye daughters of Rabbah, gird you with sackcloth; lament, and run to and fro by the hedges; for their king shall go into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"captivity"],",",["i","and"],"his priests and his princes together."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.4","order":"02.25.049.54087"},["b","4"],"Wherefore gloriest thou in the valleys, thy flowing valley, O backsliding daughter? that trusted in her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"treasures"],",",["i","saying,"],"Who shall come unto me?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.5","order":"02.25.049.54088"},["b","5"],"Behold, I will bring a fear upon thee, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"of hosts, from all those that be about thee; and ye shall be driven out every man right forth; and none shall gather up him that wandereth."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.6","order":"02.25.049.54089"},["b","6"],"And afterward I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"bring again"],"the captivity of the children of Ammon, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.7","order":"02.25.049.54090"},["b","7"],"¶Concerning",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Edom"],", thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts;",["i","Is"],"wisdom no more in Teman? is counsel perished from the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"prudent"],"? is their wisdom vanished?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.8","order":"02.25.049.54091"},["b","8"],"Flee ye, turn back, dwell deep, O inhabitants of Dedan; for I will bring the calamity of Esau upon him, the time",["i","that"],"I will visit him."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.9","order":"02.25.049.54092"},["b","9"],"If grapegatherers come to thee, would they not leave",["i","some"],"gleaning grapes? if",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"thieves"],"by night, they will destroy till they have enough."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.10","order":"02.25.049.54093"},["b","10"],"But I have made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Esau"],"bare, I have uncovered his secret places, and he shall not be able to hide himself: his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"seed"],"is spoiled, and his brethren, and his neighbours, and he",["i","is"],"not."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.11","order":"02.25.049.54094"},["b","11"],"Leave thy fatherless children, I will preserve",["i","them"],"alive; and let thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"widows"],"trust in me."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.12","order":"02.25.049.54095"},["b","12"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Behold, they whose judgment",["i","was"],"not to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"drink"],"of the cup have assuredly drunken; and",["i","art"],"thou he",["i","that"],"shall altogether go unpunished? thou shalt not go unpunished, but thou shalt surely drink",["i","of it."]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.13","order":"02.25.049.54096"},["b","13"],"For I have sworn by myself, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Bozrah"],"shall become a desolation, a reproach, a waste, and a curse; and all the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"cities"],"thereof shall be perpetual wastes."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.14","order":"02.25.049.54097"},["b","14"],"I have heard a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"rumour"],"from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and an ambassador is sent unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"heathen"],",",["i","saying,"],"Gather ye together, and come against her, and rise up to the battle."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.15","order":"02.25.049.54098"},["b","15"],"For, lo, I will make thee small among the heathen,",["i","and"],"despised among men."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.16","order":"02.25.049.54099"},["b","16"],"Thy terribleness hath deceived thee,",["i","and"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"pride"],"of thine heart, O thou that dwellest in the clefts of the rock, that holdest the height of the hill: though thou shouldest make thy nest as high as the eagle, I will bring thee down from thence, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.17","order":"02.25.049.54100"},["b","17"],"Also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Edom"],"shall be a desolation: every one that goeth by it shall be astonished, and shall hiss at all the plagues thereof."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.18","order":"02.25.049.54101"},["b","18"],"As in the overthrow of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Sodom"],"and Gomorrah and the neighbour",["i","cities"],"thereof, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", no man shall abide there, neither shall a son of man dwell in it."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.19","order":"02.25.049.54102"},["b","19"],"Behold, he shall come up like a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"lion"],"from the swelling of Jordan against the habitation of the strong: but I will suddenly make him run away from her: and who",["i","is"],"a chosen",["i","man, that"],"I may appoint over her? for who",["i","is"],"like me? and who will appoint me the time? and who",["i","is"],"that shepherd that will stand before me?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.20","order":"02.25.049.54103"},["b","20"],"Therefore hear the counsel of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that he hath taken against Edom; and his purposes, that he hath purposed against the inhabitants of Teman: Surely the least of the flock shall draw them out: surely he shall make their habitations desolate with them."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.21","order":"02.25.049.54104"},["b","21"],"The earth is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"moved"],"at the noise of their fall, at the cry the noise thereof was heard in the Red sea."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.22","order":"02.25.049.54105"},["b","22"],"Behold, he shall come up and fly as the eagle, and spread his wings over Bozrah: and at that day shall the heart of the mighty men of Edom be as the heart of a woman in her pangs."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.23","order":"02.25.049.54106"},["b","23"],"¶Concerning Damascus. Hamath is confounded, and Arpad: for they have heard evil tidings: they are fainthearted;",["i","there is"],"sorrow on the sea; it cannot be quiet."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.24","order":"02.25.049.54107"},["b","24"],"Damascus is waxed feeble,",["i","and"],"turneth herself to flee, and fear hath seized on",["i","her:"],"anguish and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"sorrows"],"have taken her, as a woman in travail."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.25","order":"02.25.049.54108"},["b","25"],"How is the city of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"praise"],"not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"left"],", the city of my joy!"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.26","order":"02.25.049.54109"},["b","26"],"Therefore her young men shall fall in her streets, and all the men of war shall be cut off in that day, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.27","order":"02.25.049.54110"},["b","27"],"And I will kindle a fire in the wall of Damascus, and it shall consume the palaces of Ben-hadad."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.28","order":"02.25.049.54111"},["b","28"],"¶Concerning",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"Kedar"],", and concerning the kingdoms of Hazor, which Nebuchadrezzar king of Babylon shall smite, thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Arise ye, go up to Kedar, and spoil the men of the east."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.29","order":"02.25.049.54112"},["b","29"],"Their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"tents"],"and their flocks shall they take away: they shall take to themselves their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"curtains"],", and all their vessels, and their camels; and they shall cry unto them,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_29c"},"Fear"],["i","is"],"on every side."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.30","order":"02.25.049.54113"},["b","30"],"¶Flee, get you far off, dwell deep, O ye inhabitants of Hazor, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"Nebuchadrezzar"],"king of Babylon hath taken counsel against you, and hath conceived a purpose against you."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.31","order":"02.25.049.54114"},["b","31"],"Arise, get you up unto the wealthy nation, that dwelleth without care, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", which have neither gates nor bars,",["i","which"],"dwell alone."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.32","order":"02.25.049.54115"},["b","32"],"And their camels shall be a booty, and the multitude of their cattle a spoil: and I will scatter into all winds them",["i","that are"],"in the utmost corners; and I will bring their calamity from all sides thereof, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.33","order":"02.25.049.54116"},["b","33"],"And Hazor shall be a dwelling for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"dragons"],",",["i","and"],"a desolation for ever: there shall no man abide there, nor",["i","any"],"son of man dwell in it."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.34","order":"02.25.049.54117"},["b","34"],"¶The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that came to Jeremiah the prophet against",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"Elam"],"in the beginning of the reign of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"Zedekiah"],"king of Judah, saying,"],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.35","order":"02.25.049.54118"},["b","35"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; Behold, I will break the bow of Elam, the chief of their might."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.36","order":"02.25.049.54119"},["b","36"],"And upon Elam will I bring the four winds from the four",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"quarters"],"of heaven, and will scatter them toward all those winds; and there shall be no nation whither the outcasts of Elam shall not come."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.37","order":"02.25.049.54120"},["b","37"],"For I will cause Elam to be dismayed before their enemies, and before them that seek their life: and I will bring",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"evil"],"upon them,",["i","even"],"my fierce anger, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and I will send the sword after them, till I have consumed them:"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.38","order":"02.25.049.54121"},["b","38"],"And I will set my throne in Elam, and will destroy from thence the king and the princes, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.39","order":"02.25.049.54122"},["b","39"],"¶But it shall come to pass in the latter days,",["i","that"],"I will bring again the captivity of Elam, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.2a","order":"02.25.049.54123"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.20"},"Ezek. 21:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/25.5.4-5"},"25:5 (4–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.14"},"Amos 1:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.2b","order":"02.25.049.54125"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.28"},"Ezek. 21:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.2c","order":"02.25.049.54127"},["b","2c"],["span.small","OR"],"villages."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.3a","order":"02.25.049.54129"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.7"},"Jer. 48:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.4a","order":"02.25.049.54131"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/7.6"},"Alma 7:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.6a","order":"02.25.049.54133"},["b","6a"],["span.small","OR"],"turn away, remove."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.7a","order":"02.25.049.54135"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/36.1"},"Gen. 36:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.21"},"Jer. 25:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.21"},"Lam. 4:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/25.13.12-14"},"Ezek. 25:13 (12–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.11"},"Amos 1:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.1.1-14"},"Obad. 1:1 (1–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.7b","order":"02.25.049.54137"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prudence"},"TG Prudence"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.9a","order":"02.25.049.54139"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.5"},"Obad. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.10a","order":"02.25.049.54141"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/36.43"},"Gen. 36:43"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.10b","order":"02.25.049.54143"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.3"},"Mal. 1:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.11a","order":"02.25.049.54145"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/widows"},"TG Widows"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.12a","order":"02.25.049.54147"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.16"},"Obad. 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.13a","order":"02.25.049.54149"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.24"},"Jer. 48:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.13b","order":"02.25.049.54151"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/35.9"},"Ezek. 35:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.14a","order":"02.25.049.54153"},["b","14a"],["span.small","OR"],"report."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.14b","order":"02.25.049.54155"},["b","14b"],["span.small","HEB"],"nations, or Gentiles."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.16a","order":"02.25.049.54157"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.3.1-4"},"Obad. 1:3 (1–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.17a","order":"02.25.049.54159"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.5"},"Isa. 34:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/25.14.12-14"},"Ezek. 25:14 (12–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.12"},"Amos 9:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.18.8,18-19,21"},"Obad. 1:18 (8, 18–19, 21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.18a","order":"02.25.049.54161"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/19.24"},"Gen. 19:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.19a","order":"02.25.049.54163"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.7"},"Jer. 4:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.21a","order":"02.25.049.54165"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/26.15"},"Ezek. 26:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.24a","order":"02.25.049.54167"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorrow"},"TG Sorrow"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.25a","order":"02.25.049.54169"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/33.9"},"Jer. 33:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.25b","order":"02.25.049.54171"},["b","25b"],["span.small","HEB"],"forsaken."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.28a","order":"02.25.049.54173"},["b","28a"],["span.small","IE"],"Arabia."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.29a","order":"02.25.049.54175"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/120.5"},"Ps. 120:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.29b","order":"02.25.049.54177"},["b","29b"],["span.small","OR"],"tent-cloths."],["div",{"id":"29c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.29c","order":"02.25.049.54179"},["b","29c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.46"},"Jer. 50:46"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.30a","order":"02.25.049.54181"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/27.12"},"Jer. 27:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.33a","order":"02.25.049.54183"},["b","33a"],["span.small","HEB"],"jackals."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.34a","order":"02.25.049.54185"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/32.24"},"Ezek. 32:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.34b","order":"02.25.049.54187"},["b","34b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.4"},"1 Ne. 1:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.36a","order":"02.25.049.54189"},["b","36a"],["span.small","HEB"],"ends or extremities."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.37a","order":"02.25.049.54191"},["b","37a"],["span.small","OR"],"calamity or disaster."]]}
